'''Jalor City''' was the capital city of [[Gotida]], and the birthplace and home of [[Riic Mardec]] and his family. It also hosted a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] cell led by [[Lieutenant Commander/Legends|Lieutenant Commander]] [[Detta Rotan]].<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

In [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], the Galactic Empire attacked Rotan's cell. Riic Mardec's family [[Death/Legends|died]] in the crossfire.<ref name="AIR" />

